May be an image of 1 person and text that says '$1,000 to the best life quote in my comments $'.

node.text:
($1,000 to one person who likes & comments) I get asked my daily workout split: I train under 12 “ascended master mentors” - so here it is:

-Monday: Legs (the legend Tom Platz mentoring me)

-Tuesday: Boxing & Abs (Hall of fame Teddy Atlas - Mike Tysons former trainer)

-Wednesday: Chest/Front Shoulders/Triceps (Guinness book world records: Becca Swanson: she benched 601 lbs, 273kg)

-Thursday: Muay Thai & Abs (pro fighter Alain Ngalani mentoring)

-Friday: Back/Biceps/Rear Shoulders (6 time Mr. Olympia with Dorian Yates)

-Saturday: Brazilian Jiu Jitsu (Number one Jiu Jitsu team Danaher death Squad/Nicky/Nick or Shaolin (Matt Jane)

-Sunday: lay around & rest (following Ironman Ben Greenfield body hacking techniques)

*10-15,000 steps 6 days a week (Kinobody Greg O’Gallagher protocol)

**Morning Yoga or Pilates 6 days a week (breathe and flow yoga)

***other amazing mentors too for body fitness like Ben Greenfield, Mr. Titanium, Rafael Lovato Jr, Tony Jeffries, Onome Eggers, Rigan Machado and more. 

****But tracking & controlling food is more important than all of this)...
